{"tid":2110169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧：將向華為部分員工實施簽證限制","createTime":"2020-07-15T17:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T01:22:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed086fb0f75d717013a9c55e2b64b68a11637326","tid":2110169,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537997-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537997-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n35S9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=cf94ae33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537997-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=133864a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537997-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧說，將對華為等中國科技公司的部分員工實施簽證限制。他指責華為向侵犯人權的政權提供物質支援。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在國務院的記者會表示，如果全球的電訊公司與華為做生意，就是與人權侵犯者做生意。<br />\n<br />\n對於英國下令當地的電訊公司在2027年之前，移除華為設備，蓬佩奧說「愈快愈好」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又說，將於下星期出訪英國和丹麥，「中國共產黨對全球的威脅」將是重要議題。<br />\n<br />\n在南海問題上，蓬佩奧說，美國會在多邊組織、東盟，以及透過法律途經，支援那些相信領土或海事主張被中國侵犯的國家。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國批准向台灣出售台「愛國者3型導彈」重新認證的設備和技術，北京宣布將制裁主要承包商洛歇馬丁公司。蓬佩奧表示，美國企業不應該因政府執行台灣關係法被懲罰，對北京的決定表示遺憾，希望北京重新考慮。"},{"pid":"e9f01947fc503ab1cc981fb9ec84fc6f93c78ef2","tid":2110169,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"好多鬼佬做華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6412c18a04100e270877892efbb840474287d7ca","tid":2110169,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656b73b333893f6506953605b3ae7